metadata.title: ASWGlobal
metadata.description: The ASWGlobal library doesn't introduce any functions, but instead declares common HSL Constants used in other libraries, submethods, functions and dialogues.

metadata.title: HSL_SeqDailyTools
metadata.description: The HSL_SeqDailyTools library adds four functions aimed at making some parts of sequence handling slightly easier.

metadata.title: CopyPlatePattern96ToTipRack
metadata.description: Copies the sequence pattern on a 96 well plate and applies it to a tip rack. It is used to ensure that the 96 head only picks up tips in the wells that the plate is going to be interacting with.

metadata.title: CopyPlatePatternToPlate
metadata.description: Copies the pattern of wells from one plate to another plate

metadata.title: GetNumberOfPositionsLeft
metadata.description: Calculates the number of positions left in a sequence

metadata.title: SeqEasyEdit
metadata.description: A simplified version of SeqEdit, with only the parameters which are regularly used
